00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,930
Ya.

7
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,240
Hou Chi,

8
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,730
Qing Mu ialah Bai Jue.

9
00:01:55,930 --> 00:01:56,930
Saya ingat

10
00:01:57,650 --> 00:01:58,200
kamu sekurang-kurangnya

11
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,010
dapat menikmati masa pertemuan
untuk seketika.

12
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,010
Tak sangka...

13
00:02:02,650 --> 00:02:05,330
Hari ini tetap datang pada akhirnya.

14
00:02:08,410 --> 00:02:09,090
Hou Chi,

15
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,610
memandangkan Bai Jue dah sedar,

16
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,650
Qing Mu tak wujud lagi di dunia ini.

17
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,890
Percintaan kamu,

18
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:19,170
bagi Bai Jue,

19
00:02:19,890 --> 00:02:21,250
langsung tak bermakna.

20
00:02:21,250 --> 00:02:21,890
Mustahil.

21
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:24,810
Dia ialah Bai Jue, juga Qing Mu.

22
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:27,290
Dia takkan lupakan saya selama-lamanya.

23
00:02:35,010 --> 00:02:35,890
Hou Chi.

24
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,930
Dia dah lupa.

25
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:45,680
Feng Ran,

26
00:02:46,290 --> 00:02:47,120
beritahu saya,

27
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:48,400
apa yang terjadi sebenarnya?

28
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,560
Mengapa Jing Lei kata awak bunuh
semua orang di Puak Burung?

29
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,250
Saya diumpan ke Hutan Mapel.

30
00:02:54,370 --> 00:02:56,010
Semasa saya sampai ke sana,
Puak Burung dah dihapuskan.

31
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,760
Kemudian, saya dan Jing Jian

32
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,400
dikurung kuasa yang pelik.

33
00:02:59,650 --> 00:03:00,320
Cuma Qing Mu

34
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,010
berlawan dengan orang yang
menyamar sebagai saya.

35
00:03:02,890 --> 00:03:04,290
Semasa kami sedar,

36
00:03:06,530 --> 00:03:08,120
dia dah jadi Bai Jue.

37
00:03:09,530 --> 00:03:10,890
Dia tak ingat apa-apa pun.

38
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,650
Tak ingat segala-galanya,

39
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,840
juga tak ingat segala-gala
tentang Qing Mu.

40
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,650
Di mana Bai Jue sekarang?

41
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,760
Dia membina semula Istana Chang Yuan.

42
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,290
Di Cang Qiong,

43
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:25,680
dia memerintah tiga alam
sebagai ketua Dewa Sejati.

44
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:29,680
Hou Chi!

45
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:38,760
Ke mana awak pergi?

46
00:03:39,730 --> 00:03:40,680
Saya nak keluar jumpa dia.

47
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,450
Dia dah lupakan awak.

48
00:03:43,090 --> 00:03:43,840
Kalau awak keluar sekarang,

49
00:03:44,290 --> 00:03:45,890
pengurungan selama seratus tahun
akan kehilangan maknanya.

50
00:03:46,890 --> 00:03:48,560
Kalau saya tak nampak
dengan mata sendiri

51
00:03:48,890 --> 00:03:50,120
yang dia kata dah lupakan saya,

52
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,450
saya takkan percaya bahawa

53
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,600
dia dah lupakan saya.

54
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:54,250
Dia yang memasang sekatan ini

55
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:55,290
pada masa dulu.

56
00:03:55,370 --> 00:03:56,400
Bagi betara atau betari yang biasa,

57
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,370
hanya boleh masuk, tak boleh keluar.

58
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,120
Biarpun awak

59
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,600
abaikan nyawa sendiri,

60
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,530
bagaimana pula dengan nyawa anak awak?

61
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:02,010
Awak mahu mati bersama anak awak?

62
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,530
Nyawa saya?

63
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:06,040
Nyawa Qing Mu ialah nyawa saya.

64
00:04:06,250 --> 00:04:07,530
Dia berputus asa terhadap
segala-galanya demi saya.

65
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,930
Kini, dia tunggu saya balik.

66
00:04:09,090 --> 00:04:10,320
Namun, saya hanya mementingkan
nyawa sendiri

67
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,170
dan tak pedulikan dia?

68
00:04:11,810 --> 00:04:13,120
Hou Chi, awak patut berfikiran waras.

69
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,290
Kini, badan itu kepunyaan Bai Jue.

70
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:17,450
Tiada orang tunggu awak lagi.

71
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,170
Awak pernah kata,

72
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,090
kalau Shang Gu sedar,

73
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,650
saya mungkin takkan wujud lagi.

74
00:04:22,010 --> 00:04:23,280
Adakah begitu juga bagi Qing Mu

75
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,760
yang berada dalam tubuh Bai Jue?

76
00:04:27,930 --> 00:04:29,280
Awak ingat Bai Jue yang hidup

77
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,530
akan benarkan kewujudan Qing Mu?

78
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,930
Saya akan ambil balik
Menara Tahan Roh.

79
00:04:34,130 --> 00:04:35,320
Saya mesti cari Qing Mu.

80
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,370
Hou Chi.

81
00:04:37,930 --> 00:04:39,480
Kudrat rohani yang dihapuskan
oleh kuasa Dewa Sejati,

82
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,040
Dewa Moyang pun tak dapat
buat apa-apa pun,

83
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,280
apatah lagi Menara Tahan Roh.

84
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,370
Kami pernah menyembahyangkan
syurga dan bumi,

85
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:47,970
berjanji akan bersama selama-lamanya.

86
00:04:48,370 --> 00:04:49,970
Janjinya tak pernah berubah,

87
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,440
dia tak pernah mungkir janji.

88
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,200
Saya juga.

89
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,760
Kini, saya tak peduli
apa yang berlaku padanya.

90
00:04:56,410 --> 00:04:57,810
Dia suami saya

91
00:04:58,410 --> 00:04:59,530
dan ayah kepada anak saya
selama-lamanya.

92
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,760
Jing Yuan.

93
00:05:03,970 --> 00:05:05,090
Tolong biar saya keluar.

94
00:05:06,130 --> 00:05:07,040
Kalau awak keluar sekarang,

95
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,410
awak hanya akan cederakan sendiri.

96
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,160
Jing Yuan.

97
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,480
Qing Mu tiada ibu bapa,

98
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,280
juga tiada banyak kawan.

99
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:19,810
Mungkin kelak,

100
00:05:20,410 --> 00:05:21,600
tiada orang akan ingat

101
00:05:22,410 --> 00:05:23,600
dia pernah wujud di dunia ini.

102
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:26,480
Dia bezakan cinta
dan benci dengan jelas,

103
00:05:26,850 --> 00:05:27,650
juga ada perasaan sendiri.

104
00:05:28,250 --> 00:05:29,810
Orang lain tak boleh
buat keputusan untuk dia.

105
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,410
Kini, hanya saya yang dapat
berjuang untuk dia.

106
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,440
Asalkan dia masih ada sedikit harapan
untuk hidup,

107
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,480
saya takkan berputus asa.

108
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,000
Asalkan saya belum jumpa
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue,

109
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,440
saya takkan percaya

110
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,090
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue akan begitu
tak berhati perut.

111
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:45,160
Tuhan akan begitu kejam
terhadap kami.

112
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,650
Jing Yuan.

113
00:05:48,930 --> 00:05:50,810
Saya merayu kepada awak.
Biar saya keluar.

114
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,370
Baik.

115
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,760
Saya boleh biar awak keluar,

116
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,000
tapi awak perlu janji pada saya.

117
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:01,370
Apa?

118
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,040
Terima segala-gala ini

119
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:05,370
dan ucapkan selamat tinggal
kepada Qing Mu.

120
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,480
Itu saja yang boleh dibuat.

121
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,720
Selepas saya bunuh Tian Qi dan Bai Jue,

122
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:38,930
barulah pulihkan badan betara.

123
00:06:41,810 --> 00:06:42,810
Saya dengar bahawa

124
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,720
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue dan lupakan
perkara silam,

125
00:06:47,130 --> 00:06:49,370
tak ingat siapa Qing Mu.

126
00:06:50,370 --> 00:06:51,600
Dia betul-betul tak ingat

127
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:53,760
atau berpura-pura tak ingat?

128
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,570
Dia memecahkan embrio

129
00:06:55,930 --> 00:06:57,040
dan tidur selama 60 ribu tahun.

130
00:06:58,090 --> 00:07:00,440
Sejurus sedar, dia berlawan
dengan Permaisuri Syurga.

131
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,720
Pasti kudrat dewanya tercedera.

132
00:07:02,930 --> 00:07:04,250
Sama ada benar atau palsu,

133
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,880
saya akan tahu selepas cuba.

134
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:13,720
Permaisuri Syurga,

135
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,480
putera long dah tunggu di luar sekatan
untuk seketika.

136
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,440
Mujur awak ada di sisi saya,

137
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:27,690
selamatkan saya daripada bahaya.

138
00:07:28,370 --> 00:07:29,440
Permaisuri Syurga,
jangan cakap begitu.

139
00:07:29,930 --> 00:07:32,480
Semua ini yang patut saya lakukan.

140
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,530
Mulai sekarang,

141
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:40,320
kita perlu berhati-hati
dalam segala-galanya.

142
00:07:41,370 --> 00:07:42,410
Mengenai saya dikawal kuasa iblis,

143
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:45,760
perlu dirahsiakan dengan ketat.

144
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,160
Saya faham.

145
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,810
Salam, Dewa Ibu.

146
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,690
Bangun.

147
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,720
Anakanda jemput Dewa Ibu
balik ke Istana Syurga.

148
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:17,280
Awak paling ambil berat akan bonda.

149
00:08:18,090 --> 00:08:18,720
Yang'er,

150
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:20,760
seratus tahun belum sampai.

151
00:08:21,530 --> 00:08:24,720
Mengapa Dewa Bapa awak
tiba-tiba biar bonda balik?

152
00:08:25,370 --> 00:08:27,600
Dewa Ibu, Puak Burung ditimpa masalah.

153
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:29,200
Dewa Bapa ajak bonda
balik ke Istana Syurga

154
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,760
untuk menguruskan peristiwa Hutan Mapel.

155
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,690
Apa yang berlaku pada Hutan Mapel?

156
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,880
Anakanda tak berani cakap tentangnya.

157
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,370
Dewa Ibu dan Dewa Bapa

158
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,210
buatlah keputusan bersama-sama
di Istana Syurga.

159
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,370
Dewa Ibu,

160
00:08:48,930 --> 00:08:50,770
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue dah sedar juga.

161
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,640
Benarkah?

162
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:58,890
Kesedaran Dewa Agung adalah
ketuahan Puak Betara.

163
00:08:58,890 --> 00:08:59,520
Ya.

164
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,570
Namun, Bai Jue ialah Qing Mu...

165
00:09:03,930 --> 00:09:05,250
Tak kira siapa dia,

166
00:09:05,930 --> 00:09:07,160
memandangkan dia dah sedar,

167
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,570
bonda harus pergi jenguk dia.

168
00:09:14,130 --> 00:09:15,210
Enam puluh ribu tahun dah berlalu.

169
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,600
Entah kalau-kalau Dewa Sejati Bai Jue

170
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,640
masih dewa sejati yang dulu.

171
00:09:21,210 --> 00:09:22,770
Memandangkan Dewa Ibu memutuskan
untuk jenguk dia,

172
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:24,520
anakanda akan maklumkan Zhao'er.

173
00:09:27,890 --> 00:09:29,010
Apa kaitannya dengan Zhao'er?

174
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,640
Selepas Dewa Sejati Bai Jue sedar,

175
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:32,480
dia tinggal di Cang Qiong.

176
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,450
Zhao'er jaga dia dengan teliti.

177
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,600
Kini,

178
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:36,810
dia dah jadi

179
00:09:36,810 --> 00:09:38,400
orang yang bertanggungjawab
di Cang Qiong.

180
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:45,400
(Istana Chang Yuan)

181
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,600
Salam, Dewa Ibu.

182
00:10:00,370 --> 00:10:01,210
Cepat bangun.

183
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,840
Biar bonda tengok awak.

184
00:10:05,770 --> 00:10:07,770
Dah lama kita tak berjumpa.

185
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:10,480
Adakah badan Dewa Ibu sihat?

186
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,330
Segala-galanya baik.

187
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:22,840
Saya mahu bersembang dengan Dewa Ibu.

188
00:10:23,210 --> 00:10:24,160
Kamu tak perlu layan kami.

189
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,520
Berundur dulu.

190
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,640
Ya.

191
00:10:30,890 --> 00:10:31,640
Dewa Ibu,

192
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,720
anakanda bawa bonda pergi
bersiar-siar di taman.

193
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,370
Baik.

194
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,930
Anakanda tahu Dewa Ibu
akan datang hari ini,

195
00:10:40,570 --> 00:10:41,450
jadi, minta Dewa Agung Bai Jue

196
00:10:41,570 --> 00:10:43,400
mengarahkan Betari Qiong Hua
memekarkan semua bunga

197
00:10:43,930 --> 00:10:45,160
agar Dewa Ibu dapat menghayatinya.

198
00:10:45,930 --> 00:10:46,690
Zhao'er,

199
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:49,400
Bai Jue betul-betul tak ingat Qing Mu?

200
00:10:51,130 --> 00:10:52,330
Dia tak ingat rasanya.

201
00:10:53,010 --> 00:10:53,720
Jika tak,

202
00:10:53,890 --> 00:10:55,160
dia takkan layan anakanda sebegini.

203
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,250
Dia layan awak dengan baik?

204
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:02,930
Kini, anakanda satu-satunya

205
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:05,040
orang yang paling rapat
dengan Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

206
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:07,330
Anakanda yang uruskan

207
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:08,690
semua urusan di Istana Chang Yuan.

208
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:11,400
Namun, Bai Jue tak pernah
bergaul dengan perempuan.

209
00:11:11,930 --> 00:11:13,250
Mengapa pula dia layan awak
secara berlainan?

210
00:11:15,690 --> 00:11:17,720
Jangan-jangan dia sedang tipu awak?

211
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,130
Dewa Ibu, jangan mengarut.

212
00:11:20,210 --> 00:11:21,330
Adakah awak tahu

213
00:11:22,210 --> 00:11:24,480
apa yang awak mahu sebenarnya?

214
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:27,770
Dewa Ibu.

215
00:11:29,010 --> 00:11:29,890
Anakanda hanya harap

216
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:32,600
dapat teman di sisi
Dewa Agung Bai Jue setiap hari.

217
00:11:33,370 --> 00:11:34,450
Anakanda dah berpuas hati.

218
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,960
Tak boleh hanya berpuas hati.

219
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:42,370
Awak perlu biar dia beri awak
kedudukan yang sepatutnya.

220
00:11:43,250 --> 00:11:44,330
Tak boleh tergesa-gesa.

221
00:11:44,810 --> 00:11:46,810
Biar Bai Jue jatuh cinta pada awak
secepat mungkin.

222
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,690
Kahwini awak secara terang-terangan.

223
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,210
Asalkan jadi

224
00:11:51,210 --> 00:11:53,480
tuan rumah wanita di Cang Qiong,

225
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,810
barulah manfaat awak terjamin.

226
00:12:01,690 --> 00:12:02,520
Dewa Ibu, jangan risau.

227
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,280
Dalam tempoh masa tinggal
di Cang Qiong,

228
00:12:05,690 --> 00:12:06,810
anakanda dah faham.

229
00:12:07,130 --> 00:12:09,890
Hanya ketua Dewa Sejati yang paling
berkedudukan tinggi di syurga dan bumi.

230
00:12:12,890 --> 00:12:13,840
Anak baik.

231
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,810
Riak muka awak

232
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:17,130
agak serupa dengan

233
00:12:17,130 --> 00:12:19,600
kewibawaan saya semasa menguasai
Istana Chao Sheng pada mulanya.

234
00:12:24,450 --> 00:12:26,400
Dewa Agung Bai Jue amat
menyayangi puteri.

235
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,130
Puteri kata ingin menghayati bunga.

236
00:12:28,130 --> 00:12:29,960
Dewa Agung Bai Jue arahkan
Betari Qiong Hua

237
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:32,010
mewujudkan taman bunga ini
dalam semalaman.

238
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:32,930
Betul.

239
00:12:32,930 --> 00:12:33,930
Dewa Agung Bai Jue bersikap dingin,

240
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,770
